h1
  span> You might be able
  span to get legal aid
p
  ' Based on the answers you have given, you might be financially eligible for legal aid.
  ' But we don’t know yet whether your problem is covered.

form name="applicationForm" ng-submit="submit(applicationForm)"
  dl(
    style="margin-bottom: 30px"
    ng-repeat="field in application | filter : 'extra_notes'"
  )
    dt
      = label_tag '{{field.name}}', caption: '{{field.label}}{{field.optional ? " (optional)" : ""}}'
    dd
      textarea.form-control(
        id="extra_notes"
        rows="{{field.rows}}"
        class="m-{{field.size || 'normal'}}"
        ng-model="field.value"
        ng-required="{{!field.optional}}"
      )

  h3 Next step
  p You’ll need to speak to an operator who can help you apply for legal aid. Please submit your details so that they call you back.

  fieldset style="margin-top: 20px"
    dl ng-repeat="field in application | filter : '!extra_notes'"
      dt
        = label_tag '{{field.name}}', caption: '{{field.label}}{{field.optional ? " (optional)" : ""}}'
        help-text field="field"
      dd ng-if="field.name != 'contact_time_preference'"
        input.form-control(
          id="{{field.name}}"
          type="{{field.type}}"
          class="m-{{field.size || 'normal'}}"
          ng-if="field.type == 'text'"
          ng-model="field.value"
          ng-required="{{!field.optional}}"
        )
        textarea.form-control(
          id="{{field.name}}"
          rows="{{field.rows || 4}}"
          class="m-{{field.size || 'normal'}}"
          ng-if="field.type == 'textarea'"
          ng-required="{{!field.optional}}"
        )
      dd ng-if="field.name == 'contact_time_preference'"
        select.form-control>(
          ng-model="field.day.value"
          ng-options="o.name as o.label for o in field.day.options"
        )
        select.form-control(
          ng-model="field.time.value"
          ng-options="o.name as o.label for o in field.time.options"
        )

  .notice
    h4 What happens next
    p
      ' If the operator you speak to believes you can get legal aid,
      ' they will find you specialist legal help, like a phone call with a solicitor
      ' or support from a family mediation service.

  p.action: button.button Review your application
